recommend check-in -- the go-to-market is now flagship-first with a clear descent to value/pro/flagship tiers, grounded in a real current device (Pixel 10 Pro XL, GrapheneOS). It is committed on a branch awaiting Keaton's "send." The build spine is unchanged: Pool P0 unblocks the live L2 broadcast the flagship experience is meant to showcase, whichever tier ships first.
